==English==
===Etymology===
Originally a [[Roman]] building used as a [[courtroom]] or [[assembly]] [[hall]].

===Noun===
'''basilica'''

#A [[Christian]] [[church]] [[building]] having a [[nave]] with a [[semicircular]] [[apse]], side [[aisle]]s, a [[narthex]] and a [[clerestory]].

